var spr = new MintSprite();
var timerId;

var frameW = 500;
var frameH = 304;
var framesWide = 4;
var currentFrame = 0;
var totalFrames = 8;

function flipSprFrame() {
	var frameIndexX = currentFrame % framesWide;
	var frameIndexY = Math.floor(currentFrame/framesWide);

	var frameX = frameIndexX * frameW;
	var frameY = frameIndexY * frameH;

	spr.copyPixels(frameX, frameY, 500, 304, 0, 0);

	currentFrame++;
	if (currentFrame > totalFrames) currentFrame = 0;
}

function main() {
	clear();
	spr.setupCanvas("custom_art", 500, 304);
	spr.x = 100;
	spr.y = 100;
	timerId = timer(1/10, flipSprFrame, 99999);

	append("This is an example of animation in mods");

	addChoice("Leave", cleanup);
}

function cleanup() {
	spr.destroy();
	timerCancel(timerId);
	modExit();
}

var artStr = "data:image/png;base64,";


var assetsLeft = 1;
function imageLoaded() {
	assetsLeft -= 1;
	if (assetsLeft == 0) main();
}

loadBase64Png("custom_art", artStr, imageLoaded);
